        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: 2/10/2017 Pim\n- shRNA KD of staufen (Fig.8) negatively affects Kinesin5-dependent dendritic transport of mRNA granules that contain transcripts for synapse marker proteins such as CAMKII (Fig.1/5/8) and Arc (Fig.1).\n\n8/2/2018 Pim\n- Accession Q9Z108 was determined after blast analysis of shRNA sequence 5'-(AA)GGUUGGAGGUAAAUGGAAG-3'.. Experimental description: Cells: \"We cultured hippocampal neurons from E16 mouse embryos in MEM supplemented with\"" ;
